      <h1>Customer Advocacy Programs: Promote Them With Video</h1>
      <p class="lead">Promote your customer advocacy programs with powerful video content that inspires participation and grows your brand.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>November 15, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 24, 2025</span></p>
    </div>
